## Overview

The engine compares the uploaded PDF's extracted specs against 20 DigiKey competitor components, feature by feature. Each comparison produces a weighted score, and the total determines the ranking.

```
Your PDF specs → compare each feature against each competitor → weighted score per feature → sum → percentage → rank → top 5
```

