## Step 4: The Weight System

**Function**: [rank_components](file:///c:/Users/vishn/OneDrive/Desktop/HPE/HPE-TEAM-6/core/similarity.py#L79-L117)

The weight is a **scaling multiplier** on each feature's score. Higher weight = more influence on the final percentage.

```python
for feature, user_val in user_extracted_specs.items():
    weight = feature_weights.get(feature, 10)  # Default = 10 if user didn't set a slider
    max_possible_score += weight                # Track theoretical maximum

    score = calculate_feature_score(user_val, comp_val, weight)
    total_score += score

final_percentage = (total_score / max_possible_score) × 100
```

